# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci, build
# Scope: auth, editor, ai, db, api, ui, deploy, etc.
# Subject: Imperative mood, present tense, no period, max 50 chars
#
# Body: What and why, not how. Wrap at 72 characters.
#
# Footer: Reference issues, breaking changes
# Examples:
# Closes #123
# Fixes #456  
# BREAKING CHANGE: API endpoint structure changed
#
# Example commits:
# feat(auth): add LinkedIn OAuth integration
# fix(editor): resolve preview refresh issue
# docs(api): add authentication endpoints
# style: fix linting errors in components
# refactor(ai): extract prompt templates
# perf(db): optimize portfolio queries
# test(auth): add OAuth flow tests
# chore(deps): update dependencies
# ci: add automated testing workflow